\ip Yoohana akaand…®ka …®nyar Čbha y…®n Č k Čm Čkari w Čn Č ar Čbhw…®rw…® na abhaana bhaaz…®. K Čh…®t…®ra amang ľana gayo enzobhooro yaku yaar…® risengerero. Ak Čmara akabhuga, …®nyar Čbha yiyo yaar…® ig Čr Č wa abhiisirirya bh Č Čsi. M Čnyar Čbha ya kabh…®r…®, Yoohana arang ľeha koha umw Čy Č abhiisirirya korereke bhiikar…® ku kutuna amaheene n Č  Čbh Čs…®…®gi. Kwik…® arang ľeha k Čbharecha ig Čr Č wa abhiija bh Č  Čr Čr…®m…®. Arabhakandikija abhiisirirya bhabh…® abhaangariri na bhiikar…® mubhwisirirya bhwa amaheene.
\c 1
\s1 Amakeeren ľya
\p 
\v 1 Iny…® umwimiiririri wa risengerero, n…®rakwand…®k…®ra aw…® umusubhaati w Čn Č  Čr Čbhw…®rw…® na Mungu, hamw…®mw…® na abhaana bhaaz Č\f + \fr 1:1 \fk Umusubhaati w Čn Č  Čr Čbhw…®rw…® na Mungu, hamw…®mw…® na abhaana bhaaz Č\ft , enzobhooro yaku ni‚ÄĎrisengerero irebhe hamw…®mw…® na abhiisirirya bhaaz…®.\f* bhan Č n…®s…®…®gir…® k Čmaheene. ∆ótar…® inyimwene, nawe na abhand…® bh Č Čsi bhan Č bh…®…®z…® amaheene.
\v 2 N…®bhas…®…®gir…® k Č k Čbha itw…® na niimw…® t Čm…®nyir…® amaheene, na t Črakaja komenya kwa kemerano.
\p 
\v 3 ∆óbh…®g Čngi, rig Čngi no omorembe kurwa kwa Bhaabha Mungu, na k ČM Čk Čr Č Y…®…®su Kiriisit Č, bh…®bh…® na niitw…®, bhan Č tukutuna amaheene n Č  Čbh Čs…®…®gi.
\s1 …Ąk Čs…®…®gana nekwe ukwisirirya amaswaja ga Mungu
\p 
\v 4 N…®kazomerwa bh Čk Čng ľu korora abhaana bhaaz Č obhorebhe bharatuna …®nz…®ra ya amaheene, ch…®mbu Bhaabha Mungu aatuswajiry…®.
\v 5 Nang Č, umusubhaati  Čm Čs…®…®gwa, n…®rak Čsabha ugwat…® amaswaja gan Č gakubhuga t Čs…®…®gan…®. Amaswaja gayo gatar…® mahya, nawe n…®‚ÄĎgaryagarya twar…® nag Č kw…®ma han Č mwatangir…® kwisirirya.\f + \fr 1:5 \xt Rora Yoohana 13:34.\xt*\f*
\v 6 …Ąk Čs…®…®gana nekwe ukugwata amaswaja ga Mungu. R…®n Č neryo riswaja r…®n Č mwigwir…® kw…®ma  Čbh Čtang…® k Čbha mwikar…® kw Č  Čbh Čs…®…®gi.
\s1 Amaangirij Č ig Čr Č wa abhakangirirya
\p 
\v 7 N…®ragambabhu k Č k Čbha abhakangirirya bhaaru bhabh Čn…®kir…® k Č Čs…®. Bhatakwisirirya Y…®…®su Kiriisit Č akiibhurwa  Čm Č Čt Č.\f + \fr 1:7a \xt Rora 1 Yoohana 4:2‚ÄĎ3.\xt*\f* …Ąm Č Čt Č w Čw Č Čsi w Čn Č akubhugabhu, n…®‚ÄĎm Čkangirirya, na ni‚ÄĎmubhisa wa Kiriisit Č.\f + \fr 1:7b \fk Umubhisa wa Kiriisit Č\ft , enzobhooro yaku n…®‚ÄĎw Čn Č akwanga Kiriisit Č.\f*
\v 8 Mmbe, mwiyangar…®r…® imubheene, korereke emeremo janyu g…®taaza k Čbh Čra bh Č Čha, nawe m Čs Čng ľaan…® kurwa kwa Mungu ririhi rinagu.
\v 9 W Čw Č Čsi w Čn Č akuja hagar…® na amiija ga Kiriisit Č, wuyo ataana ubhumw…®mw…® na Mungu. Nawe, w Čn Č akong ľeha kugwata amiija ga Kiriisit Č, wuyo anu ubhumw…®mw…® na Bhaabha Mungu nu Umwana waaz…® w Č Čsi.
\v 10 Ar…®…®bh…® w Čw Č Čsi araaza kwa niimw…® w Čn Č atakwija gayo, m Čtamuginihya mumij…® janyu, na m Čtamokeerya nchu Umukiriisit Č  Čm Čk…®ndichanyu.
\v 11 …Ąm Č Čt Č w Čw Č Čsi w Čn Č akomokeerya, ar…® hamw…®mw…® nawe m Čmang ľana gaaz…® amabh…®.
\s1 Amakeeren ľya g Č  Čk Čraga
\p 
\v 12 N…®na amang ľana maaru g Č  Čk Čgamba, nawe n…®takwenda kwand…®ka k Čnz…®ra y…® …®nyar Čbha. K Čgayo, niriisega kuuza kwa niimw…® k Čbhataar…®ra na kwibhisirya hamw…®mw…®, korereke obhozomerwa bhw…®t Č bhuhik…®.
\p 
\v 13 Abhaana bhu umusubhaati waaz Č w Čn Č ar Čbhw…®rw…® na Mungu,\f + \fr 1:13 \fk Abhaana bhu umusubhaati waaz Č w Čn Č ar Čbhw…®rw…® na Mungu\ft , enzobhooro yaku ni‚ÄĎbhiisirirya bha risengerero irebhe.\f* bharakokeerya.
